 IDLE so if the Temperature Check for IDLE tokenholders is positive, $143,504 will be transferred from the Idle DAO Fee Treasury, and 67,751 IDLE will be transferred from the Ecosystem Fund via the next IIP and after completion of Fasanara Strategic Agreement. \n\n![budget-m3-2023.png](ipfs://bafkreib6v4wqcg756tn32yb252hanfwll7nxjazs7lxiblhcbhvehfxjx4)",
