      "content": "### Summary\nThis Temperature Check introduces the [DAO to DAO proposal with Lido](https://gov.idle.finance/t/d2d-collaboration-proposal-idle-lido/991), strengthening the partnership between Idle and Lido.\n\nThis proposal consists of three initiatives: stkIDLE delegation, $IDLE KPI option, and $LDO reward program.\n\nWith this snapshot, the Idle DAO votes on the 1st and the 2nd initiative, which involve the transfer of $IDLE tokens from the Idle DAO treasury.\n\n### Motivation\n[Since February 2022](https://medium.com/idle-finance/lido-idle-leveraged-yield-and-deposit-protection-on-steth-b46883a8e277), Lido has been a key partner of Idle by supporting our protocol and our new primitive, Perpetual Yield Tranches, to scale and grow with new liquidity providers. We would like to introduce, then, a new DAO to DAO collaboration proposal between Idle DAO and Lido.\n\nThe proposal relies upon three initiatives and introduces a voting power delegation. A delegation of voting power between DAOs temporarily assigns resources that carry intrinsic financial benefits.\n\nThanks to this delegation, Idle and Lido will be able to:\n\n* Foster meta-governance activities, with $LDO token holders involved in Idle DAO governance decisions. Idle will be able to broaden the current voting user-base, onboarding a reputable stakeholder in its decision-making process.\n* Expand the Gauges ecosystem adoption, enabling Lido to join the competition to increase their stETH-based Gauge weights.\n* Improve the business value proposition, with Lido empowered to offer increased APY (via LP reward boost) to onboard strategic liquidity providers interested to use risk-adjusted liquid staking solutions.\n\n### Details\n\nA detailed description of the initiatives is available in the [forum post](https://gov.idle.finance/t/d2d-collaboration-proposal-idle-lido/991).\n\n#### stkIDLE delegation → [ Forum section](https://gov.idle.finance/t/d2d-collaboration-proposal-idle-lido/991#h-1-stkidle-delegation-5)\n> Size: 100,000 $IDLE\nDuration: 6 months\nBeneficiary: Lido\n\nIdle DAO will lock 100,000 $IDLE and grant to Lido DAO:\n* Off-chain voting power\n* Gauges voting power\n* LP rewards boost\n\nActions:\n* 100,000 $IDLE will be transferred to the [Treasury League Multisig](https://etherscan.io/address/0xFb3bD022D5DAcF95eE28a6B07825D4Ff9C5b3814)\n* Treasury League will stake the received $IDLE for 4 years\n* Treasury League will delegate the LP reward boost to Lido DAO as an NFT\n\n#### $IDLE KPI option → [ Forum section](https://gov.idle.finance/t/d2d-collaboration-proposal-idle-lido/991#h-2-idle-kpi-option-6)\n> Size: Between 25,000 and 100,000 $IDLE\nDuration: 6 months\nBeneficiary: Lido\n\nIdle DAO will lock 100,000 (extra) $IDLE in a UMA KPI option. Lido will be rewarded conditional to the following TVL milestones reached on the stETH-based PYTs.\n\n![](https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard11/uploads/idle/original/1X/7e44d330ca03e87d2fd53e2b522ec81b982828d5.png)\n\nActions:\n* 100,000 $IDLE will be transferred to the [Treasury League Multisig](https://etherscan.io/address/0xFb3bD022D5DAcF95eE28a6B07825D4Ff9C5b3814)\n* Treasury League will lock the received $IDLE into the KPI option\n* Treasury League will grant it to Lido DAO\n\n#### $LDO reward program → [ Forum section](https://gov.idle.finance/t/d2d-collaboration-proposal-idle-lido/991#h-3-ldo-reward-program-7)\n\n> Size: Between $30k and $120k in $LDO per month for each PYT\nDuration: 6 months\nBeneficiary: Idle stETH-based Senior PYTs\n\nLido will incentivize stETH-based PYTs with $LDO rewards following the below TVL threshold-based model.\n\n![](https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard11/uploads/idle/original/1X/5252bc1aa8a7837ea94a678de785e7f2c81dc193.png)\n\n### Voting Options\nPlease cast your vote on one of the following options:\n**FOR**: Approve D2D collaboration with Lido\n**AGAINST**: Vote against D2D collaboration with Lido\n**DISCUSS MORE**: Discuss more the proposal\n\nThis poll is available for both [$IDLE token holders](https://snapshot.org/#/idlefinance.eth) and [stkIDLE holders](https://snapshot.org/#/staking.idlefinance.eth).\nThe final $IDLE voting weights will be calculated using the [approved calculator](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BnH9boRmBADuyquvDMh0AmQfF97Zj76sIENKtySLU8o/edit?usp=sharing).",
