      "content": "### Summary\nThis Temperature Check represents the intention of the Idle DAO to proceed to deprecate Aave V1.\nThe initiative consists of 9 actions, 6 used for Best-Yield pools and 3 for Risk-Adjusted ones.\n\n### Motivation\nIdle plans to complete the migration from Aave V1 to V2, and dismiss the old version of that lending protocol.\nWith no Idle funds currently allocated into V1 , this is a favorable timing to finalize the proposal.\n\nRead the extensive motivations and quantitative rationale [here](https://gov.idle.finance/t/deprecate-aave-v1/565). \n\n### Details\nTo complete the migration, the Governance has to execute the following actions:\n\n* Remove Aave V1 wrapper from idleDAI, idleUSDC, idleUSDT, idleSUSD, idleTUSD, idleWBTC Best-Yield pools (6 actions);\n* Remove Aave V1 wrapper from idleDAI, idleUSDC, idleUSDT, RIsk-Adjusted pools (3 actions).\n\nDue to the number of required actions (9), the proposal can be fully executed through one on-chain IIP.\n\n### Voting Options\nPlease cast your vote on one of the following options:\n**FOR**: Approve Aave v1 removal on 9 strategies\n**AGAINST**: Do nothing\n",
